raise his joined hands, and to ask (the Sa*m*gha) for the upasampadâ
ordination (by saying), <span id="page_233">p. 233</span> "I ask the
Sa*m*gha, reverend Sirs, for the upasampadâ ordination; might the
Sa*m*gha, reverend Sirs, draw me out (of the sinful world) out of
